Cell[TextData[{
 "Any time we have ",
 StyleBox["linear",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 " objects, we have good strategies for working with them.  In this class, we \
will look at mathematical objects that can be treated as vectors or matrices, \
and then examine how different manipulations on vectors or matrices tell us \
information about the system. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.870169876487035*^9, 3.8701699736540723`*^9}, {
  3.870171838809143*^9, 3.870171847846058*^9}, {3.901536290006344*^9, 
  3.9015362914837694`*^9}, {3.9017917292653527`*^9, 
  3.9017918049379444`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"ef50f6ab-44fc-4177-8661-\
57fe8e2942ad"],

Cell["\<\
When we asked participants in a industry panel to suggest some of the topics \
they consider most important in potential employees for their research \
division, they said\
\>", "Text",
